               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I am willing to plead guilty to receiving them, but I intended to repay them again—I have been made the dupe of some gamblers—I was obliged to accept two bills—they followed me up, and induced me to take these sums—the prosecutor can speak to my character.</p>
